text: Brad Keeney (born November 20, 1973) is a former American football defensive tackle who most notably played for the Scottish Claymores of the World League of American Football (WLAF)/NFL Europe (NFL). ==Career== Keeney played for the Carolina Cobras of the Arena Football League as an OL/DL from 2000–2002. In 2002, Keeney was signed to the Buffalo Destroyers and released the following year in 2003. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Green Bay Packers players Category:Scottish Claymores players
title: Brad Keeney
